Description

üî¢ This project is a Sudoku game developed in Python, using the Tkinter library to create a graphical user interface.
The purpose of this exercise is to practice programming logic, loops, validations, and GUI development.

The game provides a pre-filled Sudoku board and allows the user to complete it. At the end, the solution can be checked automatically.

Features

Graphical interface using Tkinter

9x9 Sudoku board

Pre-filled cells are locked

Automatic solution validation

Error and success messages

Technologies Used

Python 3

Tkinter (Python standard library)
